com.wm.app.b2b.server

Class SOAPException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • com.wm.util.LocalizedException
          • com.wm.app.b2b.server.ServiceException
            • com.wm.app.b2b.server.SOAPException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class SOAPException
extends ServiceException
    When a SOAPException is thrown, this class will perform all work necessary to compute the SOAP Fault string, and store it in _toString. At the end of processing (HTTPSOAPHandler), where the SOAP exception is finally caught, the toString function will return this string.
